Object.Field: LKM BICC to ADW External Table
SNP_TRT : LKM Object Storage to ADWC External Table

COMPONENT NAME: LKM BICC to ADW External Table COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.2.1.4.0 or above
DESCRIPTION
This LKM will load data from BICC to Oracle Autonomous Data Warehouse. It is using External Table method. This LKM has to be used in combination with Oracle or generic SQL IKM.
If set to True ODI will submit a BICC extraction job for the source datastore.
Max wait time before considering BICC job failed. Blank value means no timeout.

Specify the date of your previous load. Only extract files created after this date will be processed by the current run. Default is empty string, meaning all the extract files will be processed. Use format yyyymmdd_hh24miss. Example 20190508_182024.
Find extract files on BICC storage
SNP_TRT : BICCBaseKM #SNP_LINETRT : Find extract files on BICC storage
SNP_TRT : LKM Object Storage to ADWC External Table #SNP_LINETRT : Drop external table
SNP_TRT : BICCBaseKM #SNP_LINETRT : Wait for extract to complete
